Class StringMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.cbb.jprime.topology.StringMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    NamesMap

    public class StringMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements GraphMap, StateParameter
    Holds a string for each vertex of a graph. No generics for the sake of speed. See also GenericMap.
